{"id":620,"date":"2024-08-02T19:52:53","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T19:52:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=620"},"modified":"2024-08-07T03:05:23","modified_gmt":"2024-08-07T03:05:23","slug":"tm036-sludge-bomb","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm036-sludge-bomb\/","title":{"rendered":"TM036 Sludge Bomb"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM036 Sludge Bomb<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>On the ground in the flooded area of the Antisis Sewer. Requires Surf and Waterfall to reach.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>Filthy sludge is hurled at the foe. It may poison the target.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Poison<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Antisis City<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm07-waterfall\/\">Waterfall<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Head down the stairs West of the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-down-the-stairs-west-of-the-antisis-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Going down the stairs West of the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going down the stairs West of the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the sewers through the door to the South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-antisis-city-sewers.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Antisis City Sewers. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Antisis City Sewers.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once inside, you want to follow the path going North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-north-1.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path North. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path North.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually come across some stairs to your East that you want to take before continuing East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-stairs-to-go-to-the-lower-level.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the stairs to go to the lower level. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the stairs to go to the lower level.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the first turn South and continue on the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-1st-turn-south.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the first turn South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the first turn South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can, take the first turn East and follow the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-turning-east-and-following-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Turning East and following the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Turning East and following the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see a slope you can use to go to a higher level. Take it, then go to the other side and take the opposite slope downwards. Then follow that path South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-going-up-to-the-higher-level-and-then-down-using-the-other-slope.jpg\" alt=\"Going up to the higher level and then down using the other slope. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going up to the higher level and then down using the other slope.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the stairs in the South-East corner of the floor to go up and enter the hidden area to the South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-hidden-area.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the hidden area. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the hidden area.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the dark pipe South until you eventually enter a different area.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-navigating-the-dark-pipe.jpg\" alt=\"Navigating the dark pipe. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Navigating the dark pipe.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Waterfall to properly access the area before going South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/10-pokemon-unbound-exiting-the-pipe-and-using-waterfall-to-go-south.jpg\" alt=\"Exiting the pipe and using Waterfall to go South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exiting the pipe and using Waterfall to go South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start going West when the path curves that way.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/11-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-west.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path West. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path West.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly see the TM for Sludge Bomb on a small section of land.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/12-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-sludge-bomb.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Sludge Bomb. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Sludge Bomb.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":621,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-620","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/620","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/621"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=620"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=620"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}